@191  = ~Fanatic's Ring~
@192  = ~Fanatic's Ring:
  This ring was created for a league of fanatics based in Amn who despise magic and seek to rid Faerún of mages at all costs. This ring appears to have been created by a powerful mage, though no doubt he met a grisly end at the hand of one of the fanatics. The ring allows the fighter to effectively battle mages while remaining safe. 
  
  
