  Armour Class: 1
  Weight: 3
  Requires: 5 Strength
  Requires: 15 Constitution~
@278  = ~Full Plate Mail~
@279  = ~Full Plate of <CHARNAME>~
@280  = ~Full plate armor is the best armor a warrior can buy, both in appearance and protection. The perfectly fitted interlocking plates are specially angled to deflect arrows and blows, and the entire suit is carefully adorned with rich engraving and embossed detail.  
  
  STATISTICS:
  Armour Class: 1
  Weight: 70
  Requires: 15 Strength~
@281  = ~Full plate armor is the best amour a warrior can buy, both in appearance and protection. Enchanted to be +4 amour, there is no doubt that this set of amour is mighty powerful. Forged in the city of Athkatla by the ArchMage <CHARNAME>, this magical plate grants massive protections from physical attacks. However, the enchantment obviously went a bit wrong, and as such the armor drains power from the wearer in return for the protections it grants, probably because it was intended for a fighter not a thinker. 

  STATISTICS:
  +18% resistance to all forms of attack
  +3 to save versus death
  Immunity to fear
  -1 Wisdom, Intelligence and Charisma.
  Armour Class: -3
  Weight: 50
  Requires: 15 Strength~
@282  = ~Studded Leather~
@283  = ~Studded Leather Armour of <CHARNAME> +5~
@284  = ~Studded leather amour has little in common with normal leather amour. Instead of a hardened shell, studded leather offers hundreds of metal rivets affixed to a supple backing. The numerous studs form a flexible coat of metal that helps to turn aside slashing and cutting attacks, while the leather is little more than a means of securing the rivets in place.  
  
  STATISTICS:
  Armour Class: 7
  Weight: 25
  Requires: 6 Strength~
@285  = ~This suit of armor was created by <CHARNAME> in <PRO_HISHER> Planar sphere in Amn.

  Abilities:
  Armour Class: 2
  +2 Save vs Spells
  +2% Magic Resistance
  Weight: 6
  Requires: 6 Strength~
@286  = ~Leather Armor~
@287  = ~Fragrant Armor +5~
@288  = ~This suit of leather amour is light and supple, and a pleasure to wear.
  
  STATISTICS:
  Armour Class: 8
  Weight: 15
  Requires: 3 Strength~
@289  = ~This suit of armor was created by <CHARNAME> in <PRO_HISHER> Planar sphere in Amn.

  STATISTICS:
  Immune to all magical "cloud" spells, such as Stinking Cloud, Cloudkill and Incendiary Cloud.
  Armour Class: 3
  Weight: 5
  Requires: 3 Strength~
@290  = ~Battle Axe +3~
@291  = ~The most common version of the battle axe is a stout pole about four feet in length with a single-edged, trumpet-shaped blade mounted on one end.  Battle axes are also called broad axes. 
  
  STATISTICS:
  Damage:  1D8
  Damage type:  slashing
  Weight: 7
  Speed Factor: 7
  Proficiency Type: Axe
  Type:  1-handed
  Requires: 10 Strength~
@292  = ~This axe was created by <CHARNAME> in <PRO_HISHER> Planar sphere in Amn.

STATISTICS:
