@295  = ~Battle Axe +4
This huge axe was created by <CHARNAME> in <PRO_HISHER> Planar sphere in Amn.

  STATISTICS:  
  THAC0: +4 bonus 
  Damage: 1D8 +4
  10% chance target will be turned to stone - a Save vs Petrification is allowed. 
  Damage type (melee): Slashing
  Weight: 5
